data.description: VRM $340,000-$355,000. Come check out this Beautiful 2-story, 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home located in the well-sought after King's Branch Subdivision. A natural light-filled, entryway welcomes you as soon as you walk in. This home is the perfect oasis for entertaining. With its lofty ceilings, the open-concept living room makes the entire house feel spacious. This home's gourmet kitchen is complete with granite countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel equipment, and plenty of storage, is its center. Perfect for your family and or friends to enjoy a meal in the formal dining area or your own little breakfast nook. With a spacious back patio that overlooks nearly half an acre of space, you can effortlessly enjoy the peace and quiet of outdoors. Grab your favorite Agent and schedule a private tour today!
